<section class="why" id="why">
  <div class="why__inner">

    <div class="why__header">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Why Earned Escape</p>
      <h2 class="why__headline">
        Expert planning. <em>Zero added cost.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="why-grid">

      <article class="why-card">
        <span class="why-card__num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <div class="why-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="22" height="22">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="why-card__title">Certified Expertise</h3>
        <p class="why-card__body">Certified across Royal Caribbean, Walt Disney World, Disney Cruise Line, and Universal. Every recommendation backed by professional training and firsthand experience.</p>
        <span class="why-card__bar" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </article>

      <article class="why-card">
        <span class="why-card__num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <div class="why-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="22" height="22">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="why-card__title">Family-First Approach</h3>
        <p class="why-card__body">Built by a dad, for families. I know how to find the right balance of magic, rest, and adventure for every age in the group — including the ones who can't agree on anything.</p>
        <span class="why-card__bar" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </article>

      <article class="why-card">
        <span class="why-card__num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <div class="why-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="22" height="22">
            <rect x="1" y="4" width="22" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="1" y1="10" x2="23" y2="10"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="why-card__title">No Added Cost — Ever</h3>
        <p class="why-card__body">Travel advisors are paid by suppliers, not clients. You pay the same price you would booking direct — and you get expert guidance, advocacy, and someone watching out for you.</p>
        <span class="why-card__bar" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </article>

      <article class="why-card">
        <span class="why-card__num" aria-hidden="true">04</span>
        <div class="why-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="22" height="22">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="why-card__title">Time Back in Your Life</h3>
        <p class="why-card__body">Disney and Royal Caribbean planning is a part-time job if you do it yourself. I handle every detail — dining reservations, room categories, port logistics — so you just show up and enjoy.</p>
        <span class="why-card__bar" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </article>

      <article class="why-card">
        <span class="why-card__num" aria-hidden="true">05</span>
        <div class="why-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="22" height="22">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="why-card__title">Protected Peace of Mind</h3>
        <p class="why-card__body">If something goes wrong before or during your trip, you have a professional advocate working for you — not a chatbot and a three-hour hold queue.</p>
        <span class="why-card__bar" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </article>

      <article class="why-card">
        <span class="why-card__num" aria-hidden="true">06</span>
        <div class="why-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" width="22" height="22">
            <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="why-card__title">Firsthand Experience</h3>
        <p class="why-card__body">I've sailed Royal Caribbean with young kids, teens, and as a couple. I've navigated Disney World with every age. My recommendations don't come from a brochure — they come from being there.</p>
        <span class="why-card__bar" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </article>

    </div>

    <div class="why__callout">
      <blockquote class="why__callout-quote">
        "Using a travel advisor costs you nothing extra. Not using one costs you time, stress, and missed opportunities."
      </blockquote>
      <a href="{{ site.links.consultation }}" class="btn btn--gold" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Book Free Consultation
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
